1. Upload any .csv file using the uploader.

2. The app automatically reads and cleans the column names.

3. You will see:

   * Column names

     * Sample preview of data

       * Quick stats for each field

4. Choose:

           * A column for bar chart analysis

               * A column for word cloud generation (text-based only)

View your insights instantly.


